Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.92,0:00:14.89,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\blur1\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.05,0:00:15.63,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.63,0:00:19.13,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.13,0:00:22.82,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.82,0:00:26.47,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.47,0:00:30.20,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.20,0:00:33.30,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.75,0:00:36.53,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.50,0:00:39.99,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.05,0:00:44.67,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.67,0:00:48.17,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.17,0:00:50.80,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.86,0:00:54.35,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.52,0:00:59.15,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.15,0:01:02.49,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.03,0:01:22.30,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\bord5\fs70\c&H5F5031&}Mukogaoka
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.63,0:01:37.55,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\bord5\c&H253EA0&\fs70}Flower Orangery
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.68,0:01:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The flowers here\Nare all so creepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.43,0:01:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go home, Ken.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.88,0:01:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.44,0:02:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.12,0:02:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this flower called?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.77,0:02:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What will I ever do with\Nyou, Ken?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.39,0:02:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,"Sarracenia, or pitcher plant.\NA carnivorous flower."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.72,0:02:23.61,Sign,,0,0,0,,King Pitcher Plant
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.76,0:02:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A pitcher plant, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.63,0:02:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Originated in North America,\Nthey grow in subtropical regions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.37,0:02:54.35,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs125\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HFCFFFE&\b1\pos(490.495,236.833)}The Man-Eating Sarracenian
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.83,0:03:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone help!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.99,0:03:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.83,0:03:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenji! Ken!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.72,0:03:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ken!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.77,0:03:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.95,0:03:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi,\Nthey have a flower orangery!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.38,0:03:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to check it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.14,0:03:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.23,0:03:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, little boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.09,0:03:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,My sister... my sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.95,0:03:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.81,0:03:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,She was eaten by a flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.93,0:03:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.80,0:03:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Eaten by a flower?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.55,0:03:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you ask the staff\Nto look for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.51,0:03:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The things Kenji said were all so strange,\Nthey said they couldn't trust him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.50,0:04:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenji.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.64,0:04:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you lose track\Nof your sister, Yukie?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.89,0:04:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,In the greenhouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.58,0:04:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't tease\Ngrown-ups like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.30,0:04:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,In the greenhouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.80,0:04:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think the boy is lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.31,0:04:18.36,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Six people have already disappeared\Nnear that botanical garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.06,0:04:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenji, I'm sure your\Nsister is already home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.86,0:04:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you head home?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.28,0:04:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure your mother\Nis worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.41,0:04:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.66,0:04:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.78,0:04:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.82,0:04:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure your sister\Njust went home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.22,0:04:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Kenji.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.62,0:04:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you live?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.83,0:04:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Seishun Estates in Ikuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.44,0:05:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Then the three of us\Nwill take you home, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.69,0:05:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.31,0:05:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.44,0:05:47.57,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Those two are doing their\Nbest in this little apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.14,0:05:52.43,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,And Yukie was like a\Nmother and father to Kenji.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.18,0:05:55.41,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,She's all that little boy had.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.35,0:05:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukie...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.12,0:06:00.33,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,What happened at that\Nbotanical garden?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.06,0:06:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenji.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.38,0:06:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll find your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.77,0:06:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So don't cry anymore, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.38,0:06:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurts! It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.03,0:06:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They're so red and swollen...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.00,0:06:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it hurt very much, Ken.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.89,0:06:25.02,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Has...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.82,0:06:30.57,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Has Shocker taken even my\Nability to soothe a crying child?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.83,0:06:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going, Takeshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.31,0:06:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister! Wait, Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.37,0:06:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.18,0:06:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have my model\Nif you want it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.41,0:06:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Just please, find my big sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.47,0:06:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Find my big sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.27,0:07:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.93,0:07:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise you, I'll find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.20,0:07:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.87,0:07:08.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The cyborg Hongo Takeshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.86,0:07:11.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As the one man who knows the\Nextent of Shocker's evils
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.79,0:07:14.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,he is putting his life on\Nthe line to fight them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.65,0:07:24.65,Sign,,0,0,0,,King Pitcher Plant
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.49,0:07:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The pitcher plant is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.38,0:07:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone pulled it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.22,0:07:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Yukie disappear\Nwith the pitcher plant?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.33,0:07:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you... wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.57,0:08:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... nerve gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.33,0:08:32.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,When wind spins the turbine in\Ncyborg Hongo Takeshi's belt,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:35.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,he transforms into\Nthe Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.63,0:10:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.31,0:10:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi caught\None of our men.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.63,0:10:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.65,0:11:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Rider on your trail?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.16,0:11:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Number 3 was captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.25,0:11:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Pitcher-Plant Man,\Nin accordance with Shocker's laws,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.31,0:11:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,you must eliminate Number 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.43,0:11:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.72,0:11:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The underground fortress of\NShocker's Pitcher-Plant Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.55,0:11:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.18,0:11:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We've given this man a\Npreliminary injection.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.81,0:11:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He will soon undergo\Ntests to prove that he
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.97,0:11:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,capable of handling\Nour cyborg alterations.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.09,0:11:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Run 50,000 volts\Nthrough the man's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.78,0:11:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If he proves able to endure it, he will\Nbe sent to the cyborg research facility
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.83,0:11:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and serve us,\Nas Shocker's latest cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.28,0:12:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Start the flow of electricity!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.28,0:12:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Increase it to 100,000 volts!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.12,0:12:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough. He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.63,0:12:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's awful. How could you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.85,0:12:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll undergo this test\Nyourself, at noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.70,0:12:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Please, return me to Ken!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.14,0:12:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ken! Ken!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.56,0:12:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The preliminary injection.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.73,0:12:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.70,0:12:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?\NThere's nothing to be afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.29,0:12:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in your sister's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.80,0:12:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.40,0:13:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis was eaten by a flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You were dreaming, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.80,0:13:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.50,0:13:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.75,0:13:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi said he'd find your big\Nsister, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.21,0:13:24.39,Bumper Episode 2-13,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\pos(355,520)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.34,0:13:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Did anything happen\Nwhile I was out?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.33,0:13:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.11,0:13:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Lock it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.18,0:13:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.76,0:13:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought us a visitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.58,0:13:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a member of Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.28,0:13:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.56,0:13:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.35,0:13:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they were the ones
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.34,0:13:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,who kidnapped Kenji's sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.71,0:14:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Now...\Ntell me where your base is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.74,0:14:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.81,0:15:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.19,0:15:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Initiate the test!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.39,0:15:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.39,0:17:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The monster left...\NIt was told to kill the hostage!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.49,0:17:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.73,0:17:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,A strange monster...\Noutside the window!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.72,0:17:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nobody there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.16,0:17:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sure I saw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.85,0:17:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A plant-like monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.61,0:17:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It was peering in the window!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.30,0:17:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's him...\Nthe one who ate my sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.26,0:17:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.80,0:20:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.87,0:20:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.54,0:21:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ken... that nice man\Nwas the Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.77,0:21:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.54,0:21:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Mr. Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.05,0:21:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenji!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.30,0:21:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.83,0:21:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ken!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.00,0:21:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.09,0:21:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.14,0:21:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukie's back, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.81,0:21:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ken!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.73,0:21:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.70,0:21:39.78,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,It must be wonderful\Nto have siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.84,0:21:45.60,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\bord5\c&H96AAC7&\3c&H3D5044&}Jonan University Biochemistry Laboratory
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.34,0:21:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.45,0:21:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.69,0:21:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenji!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.17,0:21:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're just\Nlike the Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.18,0:22:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.88,0:22:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Rider patted my\Nhead just like you did!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.92,0:22:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I'm not as\Nstrong as the Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.64,0:22:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But you still kept\Nyour promise...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.11,0:22:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you got my sister back!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.57,0:22:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't thank you enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.14,0:22:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.52,0:22:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Kenji who made sure you\Ncame back safe and sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.33,0:22:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You searched hard for\Nher, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.03,0:22:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You even let your\Nprecious model go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.50,0:22:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.93,0:22:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't regret\Nit, even a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.76,0:22:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a promise between men!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.57,0:22:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.78,0:22:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.75,0:22:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenji gave me his model
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.13,0:22:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,to ask me to search for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.64,0:22:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.80,0:23:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ken. I'll buy you a new model.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.11,0:23:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.44,0:23:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yippee! Yippee! Yippee!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.19,0:23:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd better go quick, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.24,0:23:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.37,0:23:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.36,0:23:18.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Everyone has someone\Nto support them:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.56,0:23:20.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,a sibling, a\Npartner, or a spouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.49,0:23:23.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They're all bound together\Nby different kinds of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.31,0:23:27.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But for now, Hongo Takeshi\Nis allowed no such luxury.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.23,0:23:31.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As a cyborg,\NTakeshi's future would remain consumed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.87,0:23:35.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,by his dark and lonely\Nbattle with Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.50,0:23:41.09,Cont,,0,0,0,,{\blur.8\fad(0,480)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.75,0:23:43.76,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,496.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.75,0:23:45.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.78,0:23:47.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the monstrous Mantis Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.83,0:23:50.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A series of mysterious\Nearthquakes...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.17,0:23:52.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Could Shocker be behind\Nthese, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.58,0:23:56.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With a bigger earthquake on the\Nway, Rider rises to stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.54,0:23:58.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week\Nfor more Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.79,0:23:59.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,in "The Monstrous Mantis Man."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.02,0:24:11.86,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.44,0:24:14.45,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.45,0:24:16.41,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.41,0:24:19.45,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the\Nvillains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.95,0:24:21.83,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.83,0:24:23.70,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.70,0:24:25.50,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.50,0:24:26.83,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.29,0:24:29.33,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.38,0:24:35.05,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with\Nall of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.05,0:24:38.64,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.64,0:24:42.22,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.72,0:24:46.48,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!